<hr><a name="_details"></a><h2>Detailed Description</h2>
Interface with a mouse. 
<p>
This interface provides direct access to mouse state (buttons state and absolute position on screen of the pointer). It can also be 'grabbed' to avoid mouse events to be send to other applications while the current program is running.
<p>
